# Engage or disengage live leader-follow formation tracking — Phase 2.5a (ADR 0008).
#
# Slot 0 (drone_0) is the operator-flown leader; followers 1..N-1 shadow the
# leader's *live* MAVROS pose, re-placing the formation around it every control
# tick. The formation heading tracks the leader's live yaw, so the diamond
# stays oriented with the leader as it turns. A follower-side watchdog holds
# position if the leader pose goes stale (PLAN section D, Phase 2.5a).
bool enable
string formation_name      # diamond | vee | column | line  (used when enable=true)
float32 spacing_m          # metres between adjacent slots   (used when enable=true)
---
bool success
string message
